Package com.ftp.client

Class FTPClientUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • com.ftp.client.FTPClientUI

  • public class FTPClientUI
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class is user interface for FTPClient. It contains input fields, areas, buttons for easier usage of FTP commands, but also there is terminal which can be used for executing commands directly to FTPServer. This user interface executes same commands in background (like FTPCommand.GET,FTPCommand.PUT... to make easier usage of this client.
